1. *Kris* je izuzetno lep i skupocen kamen. (The *Kris* is an exceptionally beautiful and expensive stone.)
2. Ona je uvek bila ljubazna i *kris*na. (She has always been kind and *charming*.)
3. On je uvek bio *kris*an prema svojoj porodici. (He has always been *loving* towards his family.)
4. *Kris*ni ljudi su retki danas. (*Lovely* people are rare these days.)
